A few years ago, they were thought to be useless ,past their prime , not now.

the right one :

A few years ago, they were thought to be useless--past their prime -- not now.

Caution:
1.year (y --> i
2.were thought to be --> were considered to be 
3.past their --> pa sare 
4.prime --> (eg: the old man still in his prime --> still strong ,powerful , creative 
